- Hermana.

64
00:06:51,125 --> 00:06:52,875
Perdóneme, pero...

65
00:06:53,666 --> 00:06:56,626
...no recuerdo haberle visto
en ninguna de nuestras reuniones.

66
00:06:57,416 --> 00:06:58,326
Ni yo a usted.

67
00:06:59,500 --> 00:07:01,000
¿Casualidad?

68
00:07:01,416 --> 00:07:03,536
Bastante, pero...

69
00:07:04,250 --> 00:07:05,460
Pero nos conocemos ahora.

70
00:07:06,750 --> 00:07:07,580
Cierto.

71
00:07:29,958 --> 00:07:31,288
Era lo previsto.

72
00:07:32,416 --> 00:07:34,746
Solo Ella puede decidir si dar o quitar.

73
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,580
Nosotros no intervenimos.

74
00:07:39,666 --> 00:07:42,826
Amén.

75
00:08:40,583 --> 00:08:41,543
Yo le ayudo.

76
00:10:29,875 --> 00:10:31,245
